  "description": "A long-distance view of the Golden Gate Bridge spanning a wide expanse of blue water. The bridge is a vibrant orange-red against the blue backdrop, with its towers rising prominently. Gentle rolling hills form the landscape on either side of the water. Small sailboats are visible on the water\u2019s surface, adding a touch of scale. The sky is a clear, pale blue with a slight haze near the horizon. The overall impression is one of grand scale and peaceful scenery.",
